data.description: Beautiful and updated home in the walking distance of the middle and high schools. The home is in a wonderful quiet and friendly neighborhood. 2 living rooms, one with a cozy fireplace. Double garage, large laundry room, Metal roof with option use of solar panels. Two year old HVAC system. Close to Augusta and Aiken and downtown North Augusta. Just up the street to the Greenway where you can walk your dog or go for a bike ride, miles of this Greenway system.
